            <title>[THRIFT-5221] Fix stack overflow when reading buffer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-5221</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Alloca() allocates memory on the stack. A stack overflow exception is generated if the space cannot be allocated. &lt;br/&gt;
